transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Hey, Bill, this is Kiki here from Pfizer's Core Blue.

Speaker 2: I'm gonna use your telephone number to 770

Speaker 1: to look up your account.

Speaker 2: I'm gonna read off your chart, bud,

Speaker 1: and I'm gonna help you put a stop to this, all right, bud?

Speaker 2: So help me verify a couple things, will you?

Speaker 1: Mm-hmm.

Speaker 2: Okay, so when I pull this up, Bill,

Speaker 1: it says that you've been working with Dr. Michael Tu.

Speaker 2: And it looks like Dr. Michael Tu set you up as a VIP,

Speaker 1: and he wrote a prescription for 50 milligrams

Speaker 2: of the white diamond pill, I believe.

Speaker 1: It's the AGV Viagra, or it's the Viagra,

Speaker 2: I'm not sure which one it says,

Speaker 1: but it says FDA approved, 50 milligrams, 10 quantities,

Speaker 2: the one we make in our Pfizer labs in France.

Speaker 1: And he did authorize the pharmacy

Speaker 2: to send you refills on his behalf.

Speaker 1: You want me to put a stop to that, bud,

Speaker 2: so you're not getting them anymore on a monthly basis?

Speaker 1: I don't need them.

Speaker 2: I don't need the refill,

Speaker 1: because I mailed them about it.

Speaker 2: I wasn't even trying to find out about the first one.

Speaker 1: But-

Speaker 2: Good, I'm glad that you spoke on that, bud,

Speaker 1: because I, too, can relate to you.

Speaker 2: If things were not working for me,

Speaker 1: you know, your demeanor is very nice.

Speaker 2: But if things were not working with me as a tenant,

Speaker 1: it doesn't make sense to actually pay for it.

Speaker 2: So let me take care of you, bud.

Speaker 1: I'm glad that you spoke on here.

Speaker 2: Let me put you on a brief hold,

Speaker 1: and I'll put a stop to this,

Speaker 2: and I'll take good care of you, all right, bud?

Speaker 1: One moment.

Speaker 2: Mm-hmm, sure.

Speaker 1: Thank you.
